<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title><%= full_title(yield(:title)) %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => false %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => false %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  </head>
  <body data-no-turbolink >
    <!-- preloader -->
    <div id="pre-loader" class="white">
      <div class="row col s12 m12 l12 center">
        <div class="preloader-wrapper big active">
          <div class="spinner-layer spinner-blue-only">
            <div class="circle-clipper left">
              <div class="circle"></div>
            </div><div class="gap-patch">
              <div class="circle"></div>
            </div><div class="circle-clipper right">
              <div class="circle"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- nav menu -->
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-wrapper">
        <div class="container flow-text">
          <%= link_to(root_url, :class => "brand-logo" ) do%>
            <i class="material-icons left">polymer</i> Demo
          <% end %>
          <a href="#" data-activates="mobile-menu" class="button-collapse"><i class="material-icons">menu</i></a>
          <ul class="right hide-on-med-and-down">
           <li>
              <%= link_to(posts_path, :class => "waves-effect waves-light" ) do %>
                <i class="material-icons left">picture_in_picture</i> Blog
              <% end %>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link_to(blogger_path, :class => 'waves-effect waves-light') do %>
                <i class="material-icons left">perm_identity</i> Blogger
              <% end %>
            </li>
            <li>
              <% if user_signed_in? %>
                <%= link_to(current_user, :class => "waves-effect waves-light"  ) do %>
                  <i class="material-icons left">credit_card</i> Profile
                <% end %>
                <%= link_to(sign_out_path, :class => "waves-effect waves-light", :method => "delete" ) do %>
                  <i class="material-icons left">power_settings_new</i> Sign out
                <% end %>
              <% else %>
                <%= link_to(sign_in_path, :class => "waves-effect waves-light" ) do %>
                  <i class="material-icons left">input</i> Sign in
                <% end %>
              <% end %>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="side-nav" id="mobile-menu">
            <li><a href="#" class="close-nav" ><i class="material-icons left">close</i> Close</a></li>
            <li>
              <% if user_signed_in? %>
                <%= link_to(sign_out_path, :method => "delete") do %>
                  <i class="material-icons left">power_settings_new</i> Sign out
                <% end %>
                <%= link_to(current_user) do %>
                  <i class="material-icons left">credit_card</i> Profile
                <% end %>
              <% else %>
                <%= link_to(sign_in_path) do %>
                  <i class="material-icons left">input</i> Sign in
                <% end %>
              <% end %>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link_to(blogger_path) do %>
                <i class="material-icons left">perm_identity</i> Blogger
              <% end %>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= link_to(posts_path) do %>
                <i class="material-icons left">picture_in_picture</i> Blog
              <% end %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <% if has_flash() %>
    <!-- notice box -->
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="card-panel <%= set_notice_type(flash) %> lighten-3 white-text">
          <ul id="list_notice">
            <% set_message(flash).each do |message|%>
              <li><%= message %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>

    <%= yield %>

    <!-- footer -->
    <footer id="footer" class="page-footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col l6 s12">
            <h5 class="white-text flow-text">Demo App</h5>
            <p class="grey-text text-lighten-4 ">
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer ac condimentum dolor. Donec congue vehicula venenatis. Curabitur cursus ullamcorper efficitur. Aliquam condimentum libero eu tortor efficitur hendrerit. Maecenas commodo sodales ante, in auctor justo vestibulum non.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col l4 offset-l2 s12">
            <h5 class="white-text flow-text">Latest Blog</h5>
            <ul>
              <% if last_blog_post %>
                <% last_blog_post.each do |last_post| %>
                  <li><%= link_to truncate(strip_tags(last_post.title), :length => 50 ), last_post ,  :class => 'grey-text text-lighten-3' %></li>
                <% end %>
              <% end %>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copyright">
        <div class="container">
          Â© 2016 Copyright by Framgia Viet Nam
          <%= link_to 'Blog', posts_path , :class => 'grey-text text-lighten-4 right'  %>
          <%= link_to('Blogger', blogger_path , :class => 'grey-text text-lighten-4 right') %>
           <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to('Sign out', sign_out_path , :class => 'grey-text text-lighten-4 right', method: "delete" ) %>
           <% else %>
            <%= link_to('Sign in', sign_in_path , :class => 'grey-text text-lighten-4 right') %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
